data.description: Explore the epitome of contemporary living within this exceptional 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence! It goes beyond being a house; it's a strategic investment in minimizing your electricity expenses. Thanks to the solar panels adorning the roof, you can anticipate a significant drop in your monthly electricity bills.    Nestled in a tranquil corner cul-de-sac, this spacious abode offers ample parking space. As you step inside, you're greeted by a versatile foyer, a space that can effortlessly serve as a guest bedroom or your dream in-law suite.    The heart of this home is a captivating fusion of an expansive eat-in kitchen and a welcoming living-dining combo, the perfect setting for unforgettable gatherings with family and friends. Adjacent to the living room, you'll find a generously sized office space, a place where productivity meets elegance with its double glass doorway.    For those moments of serenity, retreat to the master bedroom suite, awash in natural light through its expansive bay windows that overlook the lush greenbelt.    Convenience is king here, as you'll find yourself just a stone's throw from the future Fair Oaks Ranch HEB, mere minutes from the retail meccas of The Rim and La Cantera Mall, and a quick drive to the charming town of Boerne.    Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this eco-friendly oasis your own! Schedule a showing today.
